---
title: Smart Chicken Souvlaki-Style Salad with Creamy Lemon Dressing
description: We've taken a Greek staple and given it a 'smart' twist! With a delightfully herby marinade, crunchy salad, orzo and a creamy lemon dressing, this dish will prove to be the smart option in more ways than one!

